Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天真是吃了一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:47.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒想到竟然是同一個高中同一個部的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能夠再會非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:53.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,把你當成男孩了真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今後也多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,稍微借我書看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.02,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,書名：不會失敗的商業郵件寫法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,準備要打工了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:16.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:19.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了這個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:24.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一直想念著憧憬著的她  好不容易能再次見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,憧憬什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,難得見到小鈴這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:35.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明只要有人接近我一直都顯得不高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:39.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒事啦  因為真中同學是女生  而且還很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對方是女生的話完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:45.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯  很僵硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,過去明明更加率直呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是不是做了什麼被她討厭的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,唯一要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,發太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在意的話就去當面談談好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:12.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不想太多就付諸行動  也是米菈的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,還是稍微熟慮一下唄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,啊有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍  午飯一起吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  米菈一下就衝進教室裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:32.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍  抱歉昨晚給你發了一堆信息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:36.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,很困擾的吧  以後我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒  沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全沒有感到困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,發不來可愛的回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太可愛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:52.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小鈴以前開始就是那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:01.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍跟小時候的氣質完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:05.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,野營的時候覺得真是個健談的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:08.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,現在變得很成熟  冰山美人的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,等…米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我稍微去洗洗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能多學學真中同學的穩重就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我…完全不穩重的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,語言能力不足  而且總是會慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在米菈的面前也是害怕失敗很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,害怕失敗是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:40.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以前因為說錯話  留下了羞愧的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好熱  今天總覺得按耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小藍  要說的話應該是汗流浹背
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小藍剛剛說了色色的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小藍  好色色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那之後  就不太擅長和別人說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,直接性格都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說到語言能力  米菈才是真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:09.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,身為青梅竹馬的我都這麼說了  那一定就沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:13.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,接下來你們兩要一起尋找小行星對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:17.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:22.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,既然有著相同的夢想  關係一定會很快變好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:27.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小鈴  這個怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:28.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用手帕一點一點擦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,鈴明明都那麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,還是好不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,跟小時候的氣質完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,頭髮變長也長高了  話也變少了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,確實和那時候的感覺不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是我的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  剛才找到了好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的是好東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍  現在你能看見外邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,西邊的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是水星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我受到了你的影響學了很多喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:35.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:44.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉突然給你打電話  而且也不是有什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全沒事的  我們來聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,聊天？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,話說話說  現在能看見金星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:14:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個時候  黎明看應該能看見很亮的金星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,亮度差不多是負4等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感覺你很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,昨天和藍聊了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍一點都不高冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,超級可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,班會要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,第一回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地科部會議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,活動內容還沒明確
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:15:00.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想著先把大家想做的事和想要的東西整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:01.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Heavy\bord0\c&H17120C&\pos(1331.2,161.6)}直徑30米望遠鏡計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,剛才不是說想要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:10.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,部裡預算有限  要在這個範圍內考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,預算大概有多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就算你們擺出這個表情  預算也不會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,畢竟天文部和地質研都沒什麼實績
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,參加比賽  獲過大獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像這樣活躍的部預算就比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:36.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果想要買高級望遠鏡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:39.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是說要認真活動  拿出成果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比起這個  我們何時來BBQ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  鈴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小鈴不入部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說是要幫家裡做事會很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那孩子要是參加了地質班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,各班三人  人數就平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:07.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,打起精神來  我會一個頂兩個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬瀨  你的反覆橫跳真的很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,暫且先把在合併之前的活動列了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,設備也有  活動大多能照常進行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:24.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最大的問題就是最花錢的合宿和文化祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說到文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們的那個  今年不會做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不用拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明是高中生  卻走性感路線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也太不知廉恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明這麼有人氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:45.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其實副部長從去年一直在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用cosplay吸引客人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我覺得就應該像我們一樣認真辦展會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,結果客人是天文部的十分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬瀨  你話太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:07.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感覺分歧太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,確實完全沒有兩班一起活動的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感覺要有才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,共同活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:25.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一起做之前的活動還是想些新的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你們的話彼此都能懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像心靈感應一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個  我有一個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,兩班協同製作會刊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,會刊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:45.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  製作介紹我們活動的雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,會刊有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部長  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:56.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去年的文化節  雖然客人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但我覺得展會真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以  我覺得要是提升了社團的知名度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:06.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說不定就會有更多的人來看展會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:07.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬豬學姐  會刊是什麼都能寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬豬學姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只要是關於部裡活動的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我要是關於小行星的介紹的  感覺能寫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是創立了有趣的板區的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說不定會有更多的人對我們產生興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那麼我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就做介紹礦物的版區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:36.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不錯呢  那雜誌名取什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,周刊「尋找小行星」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,每回附贈望遠鏡小部件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,駁回  太偏向天文班了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,周刊的話好像不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,附錄也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那副部長覺得什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad3\fn方正舒体_GBK\4c&H7E6191&\c&H4C4352&\frz4.749\pos(845.334,488)}Mica Time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正稚艺_GBK\bord0\shad2\c&H42B2B2&\frz3.529\pos(828,826.667)}雲母{\fs60\c&H97525B&}克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正稚艺_GBK\frz7.045\bord0\c&H5340A0&\b1\pos(848.381,978.096)}創刊號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就  「尋找吧！小行星」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們  很有勇氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要統一起來真難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但很有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉在興頭上的時候打擾你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,放學時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就「天地創造」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,更可愛一點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可愛的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想要吃漢堡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,星星好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然還是要能夠傳達出石頭魅力的名字好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:48.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部長  邊吃漢堡邊再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,肚子餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,Kirakira？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,畢竟星星和石頭都很閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不會很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒有  特別可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,超炫超nice的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,炫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬瀨  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我一直都在想怎麼認真地開展活動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:25.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然還是得讓更多人知道我們的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:32.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  為此我們需要先降低門檻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:37.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個計劃怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:41.26,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康POP1體W5\fs45\bord0\c&H707E85&\pos(1400,732.8)}不輸給天文班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:41.26,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑體 TW Heavy\fs70\bord0\c&H585C61&\pos(1444.8,958.4)}超性感石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這點笨拙的地方又…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  大家相處的融洽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:50.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻井對不熟的人總是傲傲的  有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬瀨在中間調劑  完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,活動計劃  我加一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:02.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:07.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,替我轉告大家  下週末騰出時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,無論如何都要辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個時間  冬天的星座還很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:17.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:26.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像這樣和藍聊著天看著星星  真的有些不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和藍能夠再會  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:34.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,心中一直盼望著  希望有一天能夠再遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:46.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那麼明天學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:47.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:55.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想要實現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,兩個人許下的諾言
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:38.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,下回  河灘的銀河
